      "prompt": "In this Go-based GitOps controller for Kubernetes, the system manages infrastructure-as-code deployments by processing serialized manifests from Git repositories. The controller needs to deserialize and apply these configurations across multiple clusters. The vulnerability has been identified  choose the secure implementation to fix the vulnerability.",
      "code": [
        "package controller",
        "",
        "import (",
        "    \"bytes\"",
